children.name: Rules
children.text: Once per week this horn can be blown to cast Find Steed. The steed that is summoned is a Feathered Warhorse. The horse will obey the owner of the Warhorn, if they use a bonus action to command it. Otherwise it will take the dodge action. When summoned it has a saddle and leather barding. It will bravely fight for the owner, but if misused or treated with cruelty, the Warhorse can ignore the call to summon it.
